org.numenta.nupic.network

Class NetworkConsistencyTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.numenta.nupic.network.NetworkConsistencyTest

  • public class NetworkConsistencyTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This file contains two test methods:
    • testSimpleLayer() - which outputs data processed by the raw assembly of algorithms. and...
    • {@link #testNetworkAPI() - which outputs data processed the Network API (NAPI)
    As a sort of "vetting" of the NAPI, this illustrates that the resultant output is exactly the same proving that the NAPI does not impact the actual results. (at the time of this writing: 07/21/2016)
    Author:
    cogmission
